query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.keyword not like '%gang%' AND cct2.kind in ('complete+verified','crew','cast') AND kt.kind in ('tv movie','episode','video game','tv series','movie') AND cct1.kind in ('complete','cast','crew') AND mi_idx.info < '8.0' AND (n.name like '%k%' OR n.name like '%C%' OR n.name like '%v%' OR n.name like '%g%' OR n.name like '%x%') AND n.gender in ('f') AND (t.title like '%battle%' OR t.title like '%dream%' OR t.title like '%death%') AND chn.name not like '%Deadpool%' AND chn.name not like '%Edward Scissorhands%' AND chn.name not like '%Jason Bourne%'
